{{Other uses|Baria (disambiguation){{!}}Baria}}

The '''Baria''' are a community found in the state of [[Gujarat]] in India.<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=S1mk5RE2Vs0C&lpg=PA107 |title=Caste and Kinship in Kangra |first=Jonathan P. |last=Parry |publisher=Psychology Press |year=2004 |isbn=978-0-41533-049-7}}</ref> The administrative and anthropological status of the community, as being a tribe, [[Caste system in India|caste]] or sub-caste of a larger grouping, has been in a state of flux for many years.<ref>{{cite book |title=Being Tribal |first=Shereen |last=Ratnagar |publisher=Primus Books |year=2010 |isbn=978-9-38060-702-3 |pages=10-11, 26, 28 ||url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=tcTz54VVHF4C&lpg=PA28&dq=Baria%20koli&pg=PA10}}</ref>

