*{{cite book |url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=BNNRAQAAIAAJ |title=The Social Framework of an Indian Factory |first=Narayan R. |last=Sheth |publisher=Manchester University Press |year=1968 |isbn=978-0-71900-337-0}}

