According to the [[United States Department of State]], [[Islam]] is a minority religion in [[Saint Vincent and the Grenadines]], with 2,000 Muslims (approximately 1.5% of the total population)<ref>[http://pewforum.org/uploadedfiles/Topics/Demographics/Muslimpopulation.pdf]</ref> living in the island nation.<ref>[https://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/irf/2003/24521.htm St. Vincent and the Grenadines]</ref><ref>[https://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/irf/2001/5678.htm St. Vincent and the Grenadines]</ref>

