{{buddhism}}
'''Leksim Ling''', also the Good Hearts Garden ({{zh|s=妙心林}}), is a [[Buddhist]] community in [[Singapore]]. The community established by Venerable [[Jian Xin]]. The present premises are located at [[Eunos, Singapore]].

==Overview==

Leksim Ling was founded as a [[coaching]] and [[counselling]] service by Venerable Jian Xin offering [[group facilitation]] and [[transformation workshops]], before a series of basic [[dharma]] courses began conducted in Singapore till today<ref>{{cite web | title = Events for September 2014 | publisher = Good Hearts Garden | url = http://www.light-love.net/site/?post_type=tribe_events&eventDisplay=month | accessdate = 2014-09-10}}</ref>

